    'Closed Position',
    'Closed Position',
    '["Side Step To Left commenced with LF","Time Step LF","Closed Basic Movement","Open Basic Movement","Spot or Switch Turn To R (Lady to L)","Underarm Turn To L","Hand To Hand RSP"]',
    '["Closed Basic Movement","Open Basic Movement","Spot or Switch Turn To L (Lady to R)","Underarm Turn To R","Hand To Hand LSP","Side Step To Left commenced with RF","Time Step RF","Fan","Closed Hip Twist","Alemana","Cuban Break RF","Split Cuban Break RF","New York RSP","Three Cha Cha Chas Forward"]',
    'Lady is always stepping diagonally back. When foot is stepped cross the line, it''s strong CBMP. CBM: take shoulder of free leg to standing leg. Focus on transferring spine, proper leg actions.'
)
