    'Closed Position',
    'Open Position',
    '["Advanced Hip Twist","Aida","Alemana","Basic Movement In Place","Closed Basic Movement","Closed Hip Twist","Cuban Break RF","Curl","Hand To Hand LSP","Hip Twist Spiral","Hockey Stick","New York RSP","Open Hip Twist","Rope Spinning","Shoulder To Shoulder Right Side","Spiral","Split Cuban Break RF"]',
    '["Closed Basic Movement (6-10)","Open Basic Movement (6-10)","New York RSP","Spot or Switch Turn To R (Lady to L)","Underarm Turn To R","Hand To Hand LSP","Side Step To Left commenced with RF","Side Step To Right commenced with RF","Time Step RF","Fan (6-10)","Aida","Cuban Break RF","Split Cuban Break RF"]',
    'Starts from Closed Position with no initial hold; ends in Open Position taking L to R hand hold. Includes a 1/4 turn to the left, weight transfers, and a side chassé. Variations cover arm positions and timing options.'
)
