    '["Toe Heel Swivels","Stop and Go","Hip Bump","Change of Places Left to Right","Windmill","Rolling Off the Arm","Link"]',
    'Turn commences at end of previous beat. Extend L arm downwards and to L and R arm upwards and to R. Incline body slightly L. On step 5, rotate L hand slightly R from wrist. Steps 3-5: arms are extended from the elbows, keeping elbows near to body. Return arms and body to starting position. Incline body slightly R on steps 3-5. Return body to normal position on step 6.'
