    'Closed Position',
    'Closed Position',
    '["Closed Telemark","Cross Chasse","Fish Tail","Forward Lock","Four Quick Run","Heel Pivot (Quarter Turn To Left)","Natural Pivot Turn","Natural Turn","Progressive Chasse","Running Finish","Running Right Turn","Tipple Chasse To Right","V6","Zig-Zag","Back Lock And Running Finish"]',
    '["Natural Turn And Back Lock","Natural Pivot Turn","Natural Spin Turn","Natural Turn With Hesitation","Natural Turn","Rumba Cross"]',
    'Difference between a Pivot Turn and a Spin Turn is that there is no Rise in Pivot Turn. There is Rise (and brush) in Spin Turn. At corner: turn 3/8 to face DW on new LOD. Turn amount is up to 1/2 to face BLOD, followed by any Natural figure.'
)
