    '3be0fef8-af96-301f-a5b4-daff9b9fafd8',
    'Rise e/o Brush step. Up Feel the left hip is dancing across inside edge of left foot. Keep head very left, feel like dancing rib cage across the feet. Hold diagonal extra shaping for the 2 steps. Push off standing leg to move. Do not take upper body back too fast. Take everything through lower center. Lower center move faster than upper center. Keep counter balance in the Man''s arms, leave arms to Man, as you swing rightwards. Pull center back.',
