    'b71dfd89-bda5-3859-8210-09ba33da59ec',
    'By the book, it is "side, slightly fwd". It''s more of a rocking action with a side aspect. This figure will add torsion and windup. The intention is not to move forward, though some coaches prefer big back steps to really move and cover more distance.',
