                    'Closed Position',
                    '["Basic Weave","Bounce Fallaway with Weave Ending","Closed Impetus and Feather Finish","Fallaway Reverse and Slip Pivot","Feather Step","Hover Cross","Hover Feather","Natural Hover Telemark","Natural Telemark","Natural Twist Turn","Natural Weave","Natural Zig-Zag from PP","Open Telemark and Feather Ending","Open Telemark","Natural Turn","Outside Swivel and Feather Ending","Reverse Turn","Top Spin","Weave from PP"]',
                    '["Change Of Direction","Hover Telemark","Reverse Wave","Fallaway Reverse and Slip Pivot","Basic Weave (At corner)","Open Telemark and Feather Ending (At corner)"]',
                    'Different timings that can be used on this figure: SQQS, SQQ&, SQ&Q, S&QQ, QQQQ. (S: 2 beats, Q: 1 beat, &: 1/2 beat)
When this figure is danced into corner, start DW or LOD to follow with a Reverse figure, DC of new LOD.
Depending on the previous alignment and choreography, e.g. if starting DW into corner, the 2nd step could be taken diagonal (instead of moving along LOD)'
                )
