    '["Running Right Turn","Natural Turn And Back Lock","Natural Pivot Turn","Natural Spin Turn","Natural Turn With Hesitation","Natural Turn","Quarter Turn to Right","Forward Lock","Four Quick Run (at corner","LF back with Lady OP","TH","S","into Four Quick Run)","V6 (at corner","LF back with Lady OP","TH","S","into 2-12 V6)","Tipsy To L (into 2-12 V6; or into 2-5 Back Lock down LOD)","Six Quick Run (LF back with Lady OP","TH","S","into Six Quick Run)"]',
