    'Closed Position',
    '["Closed Telemark","Cross Chasse","Cross Swivel","Forward Lock","Four Quick Run","Progressive Chasse","Running Finish","Running Right Turn","Six Quick Run","Tipple Chasse To Right","V6"]',
    '["Running Right Turn","Natural Turn And Back Lock","Natural Pivot Turn","Natural Spin Turn","Natural Turn With Hesitation","Natural Turn","Quarter Turn to Right","Forward Lock","Four Quick Run","V6","Tipsy To L","Six Quick Run"]',
