    'Closed Position',
    'Closed Position',
    '["Closed Telemark","Hover Telemark","Three Step"]',
    '["Three Step","Reverse Turn (just Reverse Turn with Feather finish","or 1-4 Reverse Turn check and Basic Weave)","Change Of Direction","Closed Telemark","Open Telemark and Feather Ending","Open Telemark","Natural Turn","Outside Swivel (Turning Left) followed by steps 2 and 3 of Promenade Link (after Open Finish ended DW) (TANGO)","Outside Swivel (Turning Left) followed by steps 2 and 3 of Promenade Link (after Open Promenade) (TANGO)","Passing Natural Turn (TANGO)","Reverse Pivot (TANGO)","Rock on Left Foot (TANGO)","Rock on Right Foot (TANGO)","Syncopated Reverse Turn (TANGO)","Whisk (TANGO)","Closed Changes (forwards and backwards) (VIENNESE_WALTZ)","Check from Reverse Fleckerl to Natural Fleckerl (VIENNESE_WALTZ)","Samba Walks in PP Position (RF and LF) (Promenade Samba Walks) (SAMBA)","Alternative Endings to The Extended Reverse Wave (SLOW_FOXTROT)","Back Feather (SLOW_FOXTROT)","Back Whisk (SLOW_FOXTROT)","Curved Feather (SLOW_FOXTROT)","Double Reverse Spin (SLOW_FOXTROT)","Double Top Spin (SLOW_FOXTROT)","Extended Reverse Wave (SLOW_FOXTROT)","Outside Change (SLOW_FOXTROT)","Outside Spin (SLOW_FOXTROT)","Passing Natural Turn (from PP) (SLOW_FOXTROT)","Tipple Chasse (SLOW_FOXTROT)","Weave (after 1-4 Reverse Wave) (SLOW_FOXTROT)","Whisk (SLOW_FOXTROT)","Quick Open Reverse (SLOW_FOXTROT)","Quick Natural Weave (SLOW_FOXTROT)","Reverse Pivot (SLOW_FOXTROT)","Curved Three Step (SLOW_FOXTROT)","Telemark (Closed) (SLOW_FOXTROT)"]',
    'Natural Twist Turn with Hover Feather Ending; Natural Twist Turn with Natural Weave Ending; Natural Twist Turn with Closed Impetus And Feather Finish Ending; Natural Twist Turn with Open Impetus Ending. No upward swing on first 3 steps; Head can keep left; styling options include starting head to left and ending shaped to right; weight distribution details; sway descriptions; continuous movement without hesitation; brush actions; etc.'
)
